                    familiar faces!</p>

                <h3>Moving Services We Provide</h3>
                <hr
                    style="width: 100px; height: 5px; background-color: #34688a; border: none; margin-top: -5px;margin-bottom: 10px;">
                <p>At New City Moving Inc., we pride ourselves on being the number one moving company in Chicago, IL,
                    within the moving industry, offering top-tier residential and commercial moving services. As a
                    full-service moving company in Chicago, we provide everything you need for a seamless relocation,
                    including partial packing, packing supplies, and a comprehensive free moving estimate. We guarantee
                    no hidden costs and offer transparency throughout the process. Whether you’re asking how many boxes
                    you’ll need or seeking a stress-free move, our moving specialists are dedicated to delivering a
                    smooth moving service from start to finish.</p>


                <h3>Residential Moving Services</h3>
                <hr
                    style="width: 100px; height: 5px; background-color: #34688a; border: none; margin-top: -5px;margin-bottom: 10px;">
                <p>Our Chicago moving company offers comprehensive solutions to meet your local move requirements. Our
                    local movers specialize in moving apartments and condos within Chicagoland, ensuring a smooth and
                    efficient process. Whether you’re moving from one location across the street or to a new
                    neighborhood, our professional movers in Chicago handle every detail with care. Additionally, we are
                    the local mover who provides same-day or last-minute moving for those urgent situations where quick
                    moving service is essential.</p>


                <h3>Long-Distance Move</h3>
                <hr
                    style="width: 100px; height: 5px; background-color: #34688a; border: none; margin-top: -5px;margin-bottom: 10px;">
                <p>For clients relocating outside of Chicago, our moving company offers cross-state or out-of-state
                    moving services. Our experienced long-distance moving specialists are equipped to handle interstate
                    moves, ensuring your belongings are transported safely and securely, no matter the distance. We
                    guarantee a hassle-free experience, from packing to delivery, regardless of how far your new home
                    is.</p>


                <h3>Commercial Moving Services</h3>
                <hr
                    style="width: 100px; height: 5px; background-color: #34688a; border: none; margin-top: -5px;margin-bottom: 10px;">
                <p>Our Commercial moving services are designed to make the business relocation process seamless and
                    stress-free. Our moving specialists handle office relocations, ensuring minimal disruption to your
                    workflow. Whether it’s a large industrial or corporate move or a small business relocation, our
                    professional movers have the expertise to get you up and running in your new space quickly and
                    efficiently.</p>


                <h3>Specialty Moving Services</h3>
                <hr
                    style="width: 100px; height: 5px; background-color: #34688a; border: none; margin-top: -5px;margin-bottom: 10px;">
                <p>For unique needs, our specialty moving services offer solutions for handling delicate and oversized
                    items. We provide heavy lifting services for piano and large furniture, ensuring they are moved with
                    care. Our moving specialist will also safely deliver your fine art, antiques, and delicate items, as
